06_2_포인터활용 (워터마크 있음)

-----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

아래 <1>과 <2>는 똑같은 결과가 나옴

-----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

<1>

#include <iostream>

void swap(int* a, int* b)
{
	int temp = *a;
	*a = *b;
	*b = temp;
}

int main()
{
	int x{ 10 }, y{ 20 };
	swap(&x, &y);
	std::cout << x << ", " << y << std::endl;
}

-----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

<2>

#include <iostream>

void swap(int& x, int& y)
{
	int temp = x;
	x = y;
	y = temp;
}

int main()
{
	int x{ 10 }, y{ 20 };
	swap(x, y);
	std::cout << x << ", " << y << std::endl;
}

-----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
-----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

우측 값 참조 : 상수 참조로 우측값을 초기화할 수 있으므로 조금 더 오래 살 수 있도록 만든 것
ex) const int& ref3 {10+20};
std::cout << ref3 << std::endl;
